we've spent together.

567
00:42:00,141 --> 00:42:03,781
♪From the chaotic dust♪

568
00:42:03,781 --> 00:42:06,001
♪Gracefully stepping out♪

569
00:42:07,161 --> 00:42:10,231
♪Only then did I understand
the beauty of the world♪

570
00:42:10,871 --> 00:42:13,261
♪Why, and for what♪

571
00:42:14,211 --> 00:42:17,461
♪Holding pure intentions
in my heart♪

572
00:42:17,831 --> 00:42:20,641
♪Clinging to black and white♪

573
00:42:21,291 --> 00:42:24,121
♪Only then did I realize
that the path is simple♪

574
00:42:24,681 --> 00:42:27,201
♪It is love♪

575
00:42:28,071 --> 00:42:29,671
♪When fate♪

576
00:42:30,081 --> 00:42:32,911
♪Surges like deep clouds♪

577
00:42:35,151 --> 00:42:36,921
♪Regardless of♪

578
00:42:37,361 --> 00:42:38,841
♪What experiences may come♪

579
00:42:39,081 --> 00:42:43,761
♪Unable to linger♪

580
00:42:44,271 --> 00:42:46,241
♪Mountains and waves
are insignificant♪

581
00:42:46,241 --> 00:42:48,831
♪My promises to you remain♪

582
00:42:51,001 --> 00:42:54,681
♪Unafraid of obstacles
along this worldly path♪

583
00:42:54,981 --> 00:42:57,231
♪Worries are few♪

584
00:42:58,521 --> 00:43:00,351
♪The moon sets, stars scatter,
